1
00:00:02,065 --> 00:00:03,998
[♪]

2
00:01:12,465 --> 00:01:14,598
Oh, Robotonia.

3
00:01:16,598 --> 00:01:18,832
Attention, humans.

4
00:01:21,298 --> 00:01:25,465
Retreat now or
we will never surrender.

5
00:01:31,032 --> 00:01:32,865
[MEN SHOUTING]

6
00:01:34,332 --> 00:01:35,565
Blue Knight, stop!

7
00:01:35,598 --> 00:01:37,432
[GROANING]

8
00:01:37,465 --> 00:01:39,365
ASTRO:
What's happening to me?

9
00:01:39,398 --> 00:01:43,365
[WEAKLY] Listen to me.
Don't do this.

10
00:01:43,398 --> 00:01:46,998
[GASPING]

11
00:01:47,032 --> 00:01:48,998
[SHOUTING]

12
00:01:52,532 --> 00:01:54,865
I don't believe it.

13
00:01:54,898 --> 00:01:57,565
How dare Detective Tawashi hold
us prisoner in our own office!

14
00:01:57,598 --> 00:02:00,465
If only we could
contact General Red.

15
00:02:00,498 --> 00:02:03,232
Doctor, I've been trying to
hack into the computer system

16
00:02:03,265 --> 00:02:05,998
onboard the general's ship,
but it's out of range.

17
00:02:06,032 --> 00:02:08,365
We've got to
keep trying, Yuko.

18
00:02:08,398 --> 00:02:11,565
I need to convince Red to
back off before he causes a war.

19
00:02:11,598 --> 00:02:13,265
Right.

20
00:02:17,365 --> 00:02:21,532
HANNAH: Reno, maybe
we shouldn't take this car.

21
00:02:21,565 --> 00:02:24,598
We're just gonna borrow it
for a little while, that's all.

22
00:02:24,632 --> 00:02:26,865
I'm sure Miss Yuko
will understand.

23
00:02:26,898 --> 00:02:29,265
You do know
how to drive, right?

24
00:02:29,298 --> 00:02:31,398
Don't worry. I've got
everything under control.

25
00:02:31,432 --> 00:02:33,532
RENO: I've installed
a navigational controller

26
00:02:33,565 --> 00:02:35,265
with Robotonia's
exact coordinates.

27
00:02:35,298 --> 00:02:37,365
We should reach your father's
ship in a couple of hours

28
00:02:37,398 --> 00:02:39,032
and then you can tell him

29
00:02:39,065 --> 00:02:42,398
what really happened the night
you fell down the stairs.

30
00:02:42,432 --> 00:02:43,432
Are you ready, Hannah?

31
00:02:44,665 --> 00:02:46,198
Mm-hm.

32
00:02:46,232 --> 00:02:48,932
TENMA: Astro.

33
00:02:48,965 --> 00:02:50,432
[GASPING]

34
00:02:50,465 --> 00:02:52,232
How was your nap?

35
00:02:52,265 --> 00:02:54,998
Dr. Tenma!

36
00:02:55,032 --> 00:02:56,865
I hope you don't mind.

37
00:02:56,898 --> 00:02:59,498
While you were sleeping,
I recharged your energy cells.

38
00:02:59,532 --> 00:03:03,498
I don't understand.
You're the one who saved me?

39
00:03:03,532 --> 00:03:06,098
Do not be so surprised.

40
00:03:06,132 --> 00:03:08,498
I have always
watched over you, Astro.

41
00:03:08,532 --> 00:03:10,532
Don't you have
anything better to do?

42
00:03:10,565 --> 00:03:13,098
Huh?

43
00:03:21,398 --> 00:03:24,632
This is
an historic day, Astro.

44
00:03:24,665 --> 00:03:26,232
Soon, the world will witness

45
00:03:26,265 --> 00:03:28,132
the culmination of
my entire life's work.

46
00:03:32,432 --> 00:03:35,598
Surround Robotonia
and destroy the Blue Knight.

47
00:03:48,365 --> 00:03:50,565
[GROANING]

48
00:03:52,532 --> 00:03:53,932
Blue Knight!

49
00:03:55,132 --> 00:03:57,232
[SCREAMING]

50
00:03:57,265 --> 00:04:01,065
[GROANING]

51
00:04:01,098 --> 00:04:03,298
Dr. Tenma...

52
00:04:03,332 --> 00:04:05,898
The Blue Knight is
an impressive warrior, Astro,

53
00:04:05,932 --> 00:04:10,232
but it is your destiny
to lead the robots to victory.

54
00:04:10,265 --> 00:04:11,565
You're wrong.

55
00:04:11,598 --> 00:04:13,432
The only thing
I've got to do

56
00:04:13,465 --> 00:04:16,998
is bring this fighting
to an end once and for all.

57
00:04:18,365 --> 00:04:20,465
[SCREAMING]

58
00:04:26,665 --> 00:04:28,165
[SCREAMING]

59
00:04:30,565 --> 00:04:34,298
Astro, you do not realize
how truly special you are.

60
00:04:34,332 --> 00:04:35,165
Huh?

61
00:04:37,665 --> 00:04:39,432
ASTRO: What's that?

62
00:04:39,465 --> 00:04:41,432
TENMA: That is the
synthetic neuron circuitry

63
00:04:41,465 --> 00:04:43,932
housed within
your electronic brain.

64
00:04:43,965 --> 00:04:47,632
You have evolved far more than
even I could have predicted.

65
00:04:47,665 --> 00:04:50,432
Now do you see, Astro?

66
00:04:50,465 --> 00:04:52,098
You are destined to be

67
00:04:52,132 --> 00:04:54,165
the leader of this
extraordinary new world.

68
00:04:56,132 --> 00:04:57,498
I have a present for you.

69
00:05:14,065 --> 00:05:16,965
TENMA: I have prepared you
a new body.

70
00:05:16,998 --> 00:05:21,265
Behold, a fighting machine
fit for the leader of robots.

71
00:05:21,298 --> 00:05:23,565
I will transfer
your memory circuits

72
00:05:23,598 --> 00:05:27,265
into this
magnificent new body.

73
00:05:27,298 --> 00:05:31,065
You can keep it.
I'm fine just the way I am.

74
00:05:32,232 --> 00:05:33,398
[SCREAMING]

75
00:05:33,432 --> 00:05:35,632
Astro, I can help you

76
00:05:35,665 --> 00:05:37,098
if you'd just let me.

77
00:05:37,132 --> 00:05:39,198
[GROANING]

78
00:05:39,232 --> 00:05:42,032
I will never become
the leader of robots!

79
00:05:49,198 --> 00:05:50,332
Astro...

80
00:05:51,965 --> 00:05:55,332
<i>do not fight</i>
<i>your destiny.</i>

81
00:05:57,632 --> 00:06:00,398
General, the robot army
has doubled in size.

82
00:06:00,432 --> 00:06:02,132
Impossible!

83
00:06:10,532 --> 00:06:12,998
RED: No, it can't be.

84
00:06:13,032 --> 00:06:14,998
Atlas!

85
00:06:15,032 --> 00:06:17,365
Yeah.

86
00:06:17,398 --> 00:06:19,932
It's time to finish
the job I started.

87
00:06:29,598 --> 00:06:32,265
[SOLDIERS GROANING]

88
00:06:32,298 --> 00:06:36,998
I am Hercules,
the ultimate fighter.

89
00:06:40,298 --> 00:06:42,998
And just where
do you think you're going?

90
00:06:45,565 --> 00:06:51,232
You are no match for Pluto. I am
the strongest robot on Earth.

91
00:06:51,265 --> 00:06:53,432
Let's go!
Get out of here!

92
00:06:55,965 --> 00:07:00,132
When will the humans learn
that this is not a game?

93
00:07:00,165 --> 00:07:02,165
HANS: Sir, our troops
are getting pummeled out there.

94
00:07:02,198 --> 00:07:03,598
We must get them out.

95
00:07:03,632 --> 00:07:05,132
Absolutely not.

96
00:07:05,165 --> 00:07:09,532
No matter what happens,
I will never surrender.

97
00:07:19,532 --> 00:07:22,232
Turbo cannons ready.
Let's give him all we've got.

98
00:07:26,632 --> 00:07:29,898
He's indestructible.

99
00:07:29,932 --> 00:07:32,398
[SOLDIERS SHOUTING]

100
00:07:38,498 --> 00:07:41,298
SHADOW: The Blue Knight
is stronger than ever,

101
00:07:41,332 --> 00:07:44,332
but how powerful is he
without Astro?

102
00:07:54,898 --> 00:07:56,598
MAN: Listen up, robots.

103
00:07:56,632 --> 00:08:00,098
You've been brought to
this facility to be dismantled.

104
00:08:00,132 --> 00:08:02,598
Within 10 minutes, we will
neutralize your circuitry

105
00:08:02,632 --> 00:08:04,632
and shut down your systems.

106
00:08:04,665 --> 00:08:05,832
Zoran.

107
00:08:08,232 --> 00:08:12,565
I'm not worried.
I know that help is on the way.

108
00:08:22,665 --> 00:08:24,065
MAN: What are you doing?

109
00:08:24,098 --> 00:08:27,298
Don't come any closer.
I mean it!

110
00:08:31,098 --> 00:08:35,232
Now return to your cell before
I blast you to bits myself.

111
00:08:35,265 --> 00:08:38,232
TAWASHI:
Hold it right there.

112
00:08:38,265 --> 00:08:40,932
Detective
Tawashi.

113
00:08:40,965 --> 00:08:42,632
We have just received
new information,

114
00:08:42,665 --> 00:08:44,398
and I'm taking over
this investigation

115
00:08:44,432 --> 00:08:45,965
for the Federal Council.

116
00:08:45,998 --> 00:08:48,232
This is a court order.

117
00:08:48,265 --> 00:08:51,432
Release these robots
at once.

118
00:08:51,465 --> 00:08:55,398
Delta! See,
told you so.

119
00:09:00,032 --> 00:09:02,332
Mm-hm.

120
00:09:05,432 --> 00:09:07,332
[GROANING]

121
00:09:11,365 --> 00:09:13,998
Please, don't hurt me.
I'm unarmed.

122
00:09:14,032 --> 00:09:16,032
I was only following orders,
I swear.

123
00:09:16,065 --> 00:09:18,565
Tell me, why should
I show mercy on you?

124
00:09:23,132 --> 00:09:25,165
Get back!
[GROANING]

125
00:09:25,198 --> 00:09:27,132
[WHIMPERING]

126
00:09:27,165 --> 00:09:30,432
See? You pathetic humans
are all the same.

127
00:09:30,465 --> 00:09:33,932
Now you will learn
how it feels to be hunted.

128
00:09:33,965 --> 00:09:35,898
Don't do it!

129
00:09:35,932 --> 00:09:37,532
[GROANING]

130
00:09:37,565 --> 00:09:39,098
I warned you,
Astro.

131
00:09:39,132 --> 00:09:40,898
If you continue
to get in my way,

132
00:09:40,932 --> 00:09:42,932
I will treat you
just like one of them.

133
00:09:42,965 --> 00:09:46,032
But it doesn't have to
be this way.

134
00:09:46,065 --> 00:09:48,932
Why won't you see that?

135
00:09:48,965 --> 00:09:54,432
Astro, when will you see that
humans will never change?

136
00:09:54,465 --> 00:09:57,932
We have suffered for many years
at the hands of the humans.

137
00:09:57,965 --> 00:10:02,298
HERCULES: The Blue Knight
rebuilt us to protect Robotonia.

138
00:10:02,332 --> 00:10:06,632
PLUTO: We join this fight to
achieve freedom for all robots.

139
00:10:06,665 --> 00:10:09,332
But I'm...

140
00:10:09,365 --> 00:10:12,465
Astro, you are a robot,

141
00:10:12,498 --> 00:10:15,365
so come to Robotonia
and fight with us,

142
00:10:15,398 --> 00:10:19,398
or else stay here
and fight against us.

143
00:10:19,432 --> 00:10:20,632
It's up to you,

144
00:10:20,665 --> 00:10:24,532
but choose wisely.

145
00:10:29,598 --> 00:10:31,565
HANNAH: Reno, is the car broken?

146
00:10:33,365 --> 00:10:36,098
Nah, it's all right.
I can fix anything.

147
00:10:36,132 --> 00:10:38,498
I hope.

148
00:10:41,498 --> 00:10:43,865
RENO:
Come on, Reno,
<i>you can do it.</i>

149
00:10:43,898 --> 00:10:46,498
Hannah's counting on you.
<i>Don't mess this up.</i>

150
00:10:46,532 --> 00:10:48,198
[BOTH GASPING]

151
00:10:51,498 --> 00:10:55,965
Oh, no! If the air patrol
catches us, we're done for!

152
00:10:55,998 --> 00:10:58,432
Come on. Don't do this to me!

153
00:10:58,465 --> 00:10:59,898
[SHOUTING]

154
00:11:01,965 --> 00:11:03,932
Oh. Hey, it worked!

155
00:11:03,965 --> 00:11:05,998
[BOTH YELLING]

156
00:11:10,332 --> 00:11:11,498
Ahh!

157
00:11:13,632 --> 00:11:15,265
RENO: Epsilon!

158
00:11:15,298 --> 00:11:17,198
EPSILON: Hang on, guys.

159
00:11:21,532 --> 00:11:25,465
COMPUTER: <i>Identity confirmed.</i>
<i>Proceed and destroy.</i>

160
00:11:25,498 --> 00:11:29,032
You heard the computer, boys.
Let's get her.

161
00:11:33,898 --> 00:11:36,098
Who starts shooting
without a warning?

162
00:11:36,132 --> 00:11:37,932
[GROANING]

163
00:11:37,965 --> 00:11:41,198
I think they're after me, Reno.

164
00:11:44,232 --> 00:11:47,232
In seven seconds, the ice wall
up ahead will collapse.

165
00:11:47,265 --> 00:11:48,632
Come on, let's go.

166
00:11:48,665 --> 00:11:50,565
Good idea.

167
00:11:57,932 --> 00:11:59,565
[SCREAMING]

168
00:12:08,065 --> 00:12:10,532
HANS: Sir, we've received
a message from Mr. Drake.

169
00:12:10,565 --> 00:12:12,632
RED: Yes. What is it?

170
00:12:12,665 --> 00:12:14,398
Your daughter is missing

171
00:12:14,432 --> 00:12:16,532
and they think she
might have been kidnapped.

172
00:12:16,565 --> 00:12:20,932
Oh, no, my Hannah. This is
obviously the work of robots.

173
00:12:20,965 --> 00:12:25,032
But why must she be punished
when it's me they want?

174
00:12:25,065 --> 00:12:26,365
Order the troops back to base

175
00:12:26,398 --> 00:12:28,432
and aim the Pulsar Cannon
at Robotonia.

176
00:12:28,465 --> 00:12:30,898
But, sir, we need
authorization from the council

177
00:12:30,932 --> 00:12:32,598
to use the Pulsar Cannon.

178
00:12:32,632 --> 00:12:34,498
I don't care!

179
00:12:34,532 --> 00:12:38,932
I will make the robots pay
for taking my daughter.

180
00:12:49,198 --> 00:12:50,498
YUKO: The Ulysses forces

181
00:12:50,532 --> 00:12:52,965
have activated
the Pulsar Laser Cannon.

182
00:12:52,998 --> 00:12:55,498
According to this,
they're targeting Robotonia.

183
00:12:55,532 --> 00:12:57,032
This is terrible.

184
00:12:57,065 --> 00:12:59,565
That is the most powerful laser
in the world.

185
00:13:02,432 --> 00:13:03,498
Huh?

186
00:13:03,532 --> 00:13:05,332
[SOBBING]

187
00:13:08,532 --> 00:13:11,232
Doctor, I missed you!

188
00:13:11,265 --> 00:13:14,498
Zoran, how on earth
did you get here?

189
00:13:14,532 --> 00:13:17,498
O'SHAY: Tawashi!

190
00:13:17,532 --> 00:13:20,165
Did you do this?

191
00:13:20,198 --> 00:13:22,898
I have a case to investigate,
and I'm not going to let

192
00:13:22,932 --> 00:13:25,865
Chairman Lyon or the Federal
Council stand in my way.

193
00:13:25,898 --> 00:13:28,298
Now, don't get
the wrong idea, Doctor.

194
00:13:28,332 --> 00:13:30,998
You and Yuko
are still under arrest.

195
00:13:31,032 --> 00:13:33,398
But if you're planning on
running off to Robotonia,

196
00:13:33,432 --> 00:13:36,565
take Delta to, ah,
keep an eye on you for me.

197
00:13:36,598 --> 00:13:38,898
Huh?

198
00:13:38,932 --> 00:13:40,198
Thank you, detective.

199
00:13:46,632 --> 00:13:48,532
Hurry, Astro.

200
00:13:48,565 --> 00:13:51,265
You're the only one
who can save the robots now.

201
00:13:51,298 --> 00:13:54,065
You can do it.

202
00:13:56,098 --> 00:13:57,498
Huh?

203
00:14:04,398 --> 00:14:06,498
The Pulsar Cannon
has been activated.

204
00:14:06,532 --> 00:14:07,632
[GASPING]

205
00:14:07,665 --> 00:14:09,432
The humans can have me,

206
00:14:09,465 --> 00:14:11,565
but I won't let them
take Robotonia.

207
00:14:13,498 --> 00:14:15,265
[HORSE NEIGHING]
Hah!

208
00:14:21,665 --> 00:14:23,632
RED: Position
the Pulsar Laser now.

209
00:14:23,665 --> 00:14:25,632
HANS: Yes, sir.

210
00:14:25,665 --> 00:14:29,365
Blue Knight,
time to pay for your freedom.

211
00:14:49,532 --> 00:14:52,332
RENO: The Pulsar Laser Cannon
was designed to destroy

212
00:14:52,365 --> 00:14:55,032
meteors and space debris
that get too close to Earth.

213
00:14:55,065 --> 00:14:57,532
A power of that magnitude

214
00:14:57,565 --> 00:14:59,632
could wipe Robotonia
off the face of the planet.

215
00:14:59,665 --> 00:15:01,332
What can we do?

216
00:15:01,365 --> 00:15:03,165
It will be all right.

217
00:15:03,198 --> 00:15:06,332
The Blue Knight is on his way,
so is Astro.

218
00:15:06,365 --> 00:15:08,065
Astro?

219
00:15:12,365 --> 00:15:16,065
I will protect Robotonia
to the end.

220
00:15:18,365 --> 00:15:22,432
Astro, if you can hear me,
we're on our way.

221
00:15:30,298 --> 00:15:33,298
Sir, the Blue Knight is within
range of the Pulsar Cannon.

222
00:15:34,632 --> 00:15:35,998
Fire at will.

223
00:15:39,632 --> 00:15:43,032
[GROANING]

224
00:15:43,065 --> 00:15:46,065
[SCREAMING]

225
00:15:47,598 --> 00:15:49,298
It's over, Blue Knight.

226
00:15:53,232 --> 00:15:55,032
[SCREAMING]

227
00:15:58,198 --> 00:16:00,465
I'll deflect the beam,
Blue Knight,

228
00:16:00,498 --> 00:16:01,965
and you take the satellite.

229
00:16:01,998 --> 00:16:04,198
Okay.

230
00:16:17,265 --> 00:16:21,232
The pulsar is protected
by a force field.

231
00:16:21,265 --> 00:16:24,998
HANS: Sir, the cannon
is recharging.

232
00:16:25,032 --> 00:16:26,598
Excellent.

233
00:16:26,632 --> 00:16:29,465
We'll wipe out the Blue Knight
and Robotonia at the same time.

234
00:16:29,498 --> 00:16:30,998
What?

235
00:16:38,565 --> 00:16:40,032
A submarine?

236
00:16:43,665 --> 00:16:45,032
TAWASHI: Drake!

237
00:16:45,065 --> 00:16:48,298
I should have known it was you.

238
00:16:48,332 --> 00:16:49,898
I know you're behind
all of this,

239
00:16:49,932 --> 00:16:51,332
and I will hunt you down

240
00:16:51,365 --> 00:16:53,598
until you're behind bars
once and for all.

241
00:16:53,632 --> 00:16:55,998
Do you hear me, Drake?

242
00:16:56,032 --> 00:16:57,998
I've done nothing wrong,
detective.

243
00:16:58,032 --> 00:17:00,998
You're the fool
for trusting robots

244
00:17:01,032 --> 00:17:02,532
and letting them brainwash you.

245
00:17:13,265 --> 00:17:14,965
Don't let him get away.
Arrest him.

246
00:17:14,998 --> 00:17:16,998
POLICE: Yes, sir.

247
00:17:17,032 --> 00:17:20,432
[POLICE SHOUTING]

248
00:17:20,465 --> 00:17:21,432
Alpha?

249
00:17:24,598 --> 00:17:27,232
Oh, no. Air mines.

250
00:17:27,265 --> 00:17:31,598
Nobody move. If we hit one,
we'll be blown to smithereens.

251
00:17:31,632 --> 00:17:32,998
[LAUGHING EVILLY]

252
00:17:33,032 --> 00:17:34,965
Good luck, detective.

253
00:17:39,532 --> 00:17:42,898
It's recharging!

254
00:17:42,932 --> 00:17:46,898
ASTRO: Blue Knight,
listen to me, I've got a plan.

255
00:17:46,932 --> 00:17:49,032
If we fire our
beams together

256
00:17:49,065 --> 00:17:51,232
and aim for the same spot
on the cannon,

257
00:17:51,265 --> 00:17:53,465
I think we can blast
through the force field.

258
00:17:55,298 --> 00:17:56,932
Let's do it.

259
00:17:56,965 --> 00:17:59,932
KATO: Like I always say,

260
00:17:59,965 --> 00:18:02,598
destruction is
the greatest form of art.

261
00:18:02,632 --> 00:18:04,598
[LAUGHING]

262
00:18:04,632 --> 00:18:06,998
Don't do this, Kato.

263
00:18:07,032 --> 00:18:10,032
Detective, you're about to
become my latest masterpiece.

264
00:18:10,065 --> 00:18:11,232
HANS: Charging cycle complete.

265
00:18:11,265 --> 00:18:13,565
The Pulsar Cannon
is fully armed.

266
00:18:13,598 --> 00:18:17,365
When I'm done, it will be
as if Robotonia never existed.

267
00:18:17,398 --> 00:18:19,865
Goodbye, Detective.

268
00:18:19,898 --> 00:18:21,098
[GROWLING]

269
00:18:35,198 --> 00:18:36,832
[BOTH YELLING]

270
00:18:42,198 --> 00:18:44,098
[BOTH GROANING]

271
00:18:54,998 --> 00:18:58,432
KATO: Get off me!

272
00:19:00,498 --> 00:19:03,132
[BOTH GROANING]

273
00:19:05,932 --> 00:19:07,832
Bull's eye!

274
00:19:12,198 --> 00:19:13,532
[BOTH SHOUTING]

275
00:19:19,998 --> 00:19:21,198
[SCREAMING]

276
00:19:30,898 --> 00:19:32,465
HANS: The pulsar's laser
was knocked off target

277
00:19:32,498 --> 00:19:34,098
just before detonation.

278
00:19:34,132 --> 00:19:38,332
Sir, Robotonia is...unharmed.

279
00:19:38,365 --> 00:19:42,265
This isn't over!

280
00:19:46,932 --> 00:19:48,365
Long live Robotonia!
Whoo!

281
00:19:48,398 --> 00:19:50,532
Yay!

282
00:19:50,565 --> 00:19:53,365
PLUTO: We were
very lucky today.

283
00:19:53,398 --> 00:19:57,298
Yes. But some day,
our luck may run out.

284
00:19:57,332 --> 00:20:01,065
TENMA: Astro, there is still
time to accept your destiny.

285
00:20:01,098 --> 00:20:04,065
I will be waiting for you.

286
00:20:04,098 --> 00:20:08,065
ASTRO: Blue Knight, let's go
back and talk to the humans.

287
00:20:08,098 --> 00:20:11,198
I know we can convince them
that fighting is not the answer.

288
00:20:11,232 --> 00:20:13,132
Thank you for
your help today, Astro.

289
00:20:13,165 --> 00:20:14,598
But that does not mean

290
00:20:14,632 --> 00:20:17,165
the war between
humans and robots is over.

291
00:20:17,198 --> 00:20:19,465
It is only the beginning.

292
00:20:19,498 --> 00:20:20,365
Hyah!

293
00:20:23,665 --> 00:20:25,498
I may be a robot,

294
00:20:25,532 --> 00:20:29,365
but, Blue Knight, I will not
fight this war with you!

295
00:20:41,265 --> 00:20:44,165
[♪]

